8. Troubleshooting
- If HTML loads but JSON inside is empty, check the MariaDB query.
- If the browser hangs, verify the Flask port is correct in Nginx.
- If JSON shows as text only, ensure &#39;Content-Type&#39; headers are correct.
9. Acceptance Criteria
The system is complete when:
- All four endpoints load in a browser.
- ChatGPT can read from /mem/search and /mem/get without errors.
